text: Brianna Kiesel (born July 8, 1993) is an American professional basketball player for the Atlanta Dream of the Women's National Basketball Association (WNBA). ==College== Kiesel is the Pittsburgh Panthers' all-time leader in minutes played and fifth all-time leader in points and assists.
